l so bad about myself. I feel like I should have done something before we slept together, but I don&amp;#039;t know what. I asked him to make sure he was clean: he did. We had no idea that they didn&amp;#039;t do standard tests for herpes.

How do I stop feeling dirty and like I was irresponsible?

